<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Class Enrollment Notification</title>
</head>

<body style="margin:0;font-family:arial">
    <table style="border:0;width:100%">
        <tr style="background:#eeeeee">
            <td style="padding:20px;color:#808080;text-align:center;font-size:40px;font-weight:600">
                {{app_name}}
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding:20px;color:#808080;font-size:16px;font-weight:100">
                <h2 style="color:#333;margin-bottom:20px">Class Enrollment Notification</h2>
                <p>Dear {{parentName}},</p>
                <p>We are pleased to inform you that <strong>{{studentName}}</strong> has been successfully enrolled in the following class:</p>
                
                <div style="background:#f5f5f5;padding:15px;margin:20px 0;border-radius:5px">
                    <h3 style="color:#00838f;margin-top:0">{{className}}</h3>
                    <p><strong>Subject:</strong> {{subjectName}}</p>
                    <p><strong>Teacher:</strong> {{teacherName}}</p>
                    <p><strong>Schedule:</strong> {{schedule}}</p>
                    <p><strong>Fee:</strong> {{fee}}</p>
                </div>
                
                <p>Please ensure that the monthly fee is paid by the due date to avoid any late fees.</p>
                <p>If you have any questions about this enrollment, please contact our office.</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align:center;padding:20px">
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}"
                    style="display:inline-block;padding:15px 30px;background:#00838f;text-decoration:none;color:#ffffff;border-radius:5px">View Dashboard</a>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding:20px;color:#808080;font-size:14px;text-align:center">
                <p>Best regards,<br>The {{app_name}} Team</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>

</html>
